meta.name: POC 3D Printer Motor 1-Template
meta.description: template created from dashboard: POC 3D Printer Motor 1

queries.text:
from(bucket: "POC 3D Printer")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "Motor Axis 1")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "std_acc_x")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 10s, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")
